						<summary>

						<p>On a stone standing in a field.</p>						

						<p>Circa 11th century.</p>						

						<p>It records a gift of land to a Jaina temple of <hi rend="italic">Kaṇḍūru-gaṇa,</hi> by Mṛigāvatiyabbe in the presence of the Twenty-four <hi rend="italic">Ūroḍeyas</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Pañchamaṭha-sthāna</hi> of Puluvuraṇi.</p>						

